Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.06,0:18:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这个观点是有效的前提就是整个社会环境没有走向病态的发展.\N如果社会这样发展的话,会使问题更加复杂,而且社会朝病态发展也不是一次两次了.\Nnow you know that can go wrong if the entire social community takes a pathological turn and that makes things more complicated and that does happen from time to time
