Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.20,0:20:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,所以现在我认为孤独有两种性质,物理距离和情感距离.我觉得我已经熟悉了独自一人的感觉,我本身就是个内向的人,就是一个Nerd.\Nso I think it's proximal and it's emotional I've I've mastered the art of being alone I'm an introvert by Nature just a nerd
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.64,0:20:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢读书,我在热闹的氛围里可以同时做到打招呼和沉浸在自己的世界里.\N这种行为有其生理,精神上的损耗.我不想再因为自己没有性格怪罪自己.我想学新的技能,交朋友的技能\NI love to read my books and so I I mastered the art of being alone in a crowded room I can wave and smile and be completely on my own planet and that has a physiological and a spiritual cost to it and so what I had to stop doing was beating myself up for having a lack of character or I'm a failure no I I needed I needed to learn a new set of skills and that skill set was making friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.30,0:21:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,当还是小孩子的时候,上中学的时候,上大学的时候,一切的事情都是包括集体.\N一起玩耍,一起休息.一切事情都是集体一起做的.当你走向社会,走出军队的时候,世界告诉你,现在到你决定你要干什么的时候了.\Nwhen you're a child when you're in middle school when you're in high school when you're in University everything is geared towards Community you play games together you don't play games together it's all about doing things together and then you cross that graduation stage or you get out of the army and the world looks at you and says it's now you versus everybody and
