Dialogue: 0,1:28:31.39,1:28:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你可能会想,如果我走进去的话,没人会和我说话.\N然后这个场景就会在你的大脑中以图片的形式展现出来,然后你还不断的脑补接下来会发生的事情\Nyou know and it'll be something like well I'm going to go in here and no one's going to talk to me and this will happen in pictures like a little movie
Dialogue: 0,1:28:38.06,1:28:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,没人会跟我说话,我肯定会一个人呆在角落里,我会感到很无聊,\N我会出汗发热,我会感到很不舒服.然后上次我参加了个同样的聚会,发生了贼恐怖的事情\Nno one's going to talk to me and I'm going to end up in the corner and I'm going to be bored and I'm going to be sweaty and hot and it's going to be real uncomfortable and it's just like this other time when I went to this social occasion and this terrible thing happened
