Dialogue: 0,1:31:13.12,1:31:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我想知道为什么我上次做的事情为什么没成功.我想看看我能不能总结出原因.\N我想知道如果不那么做,还有没有其它办法来得到好一点的结果\N即使我没找到,起码我尝试寻找了更好的解决方法\Nwell I'm gonna think about things that I did that didn't work out so well and see if I can specify what they were and see if I can figure out how to replace them with something better at least with the intent to do\N\Nbetter
