Dialogue: 0,1:32:44.85,1:32:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,对我来说,写作也有同样的效果.把自身的感受带出我的身体,写在纸上\NI find great great value in journaling writing things down getting them out of my body and onto paper
Dialogue: 0,1:32:51.24,1:33:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,但我觉得我这个写作舒展自身的问题就是,\N我只是在对自己忏悔,这个行为本身是孤立的,没有影响到外界.当然我这个行为本身就有一定的价值\Nbut I think we've gotten very isolated with our journaling and are writing it down and we've become um I'm having this confession with myself now,and there's value to that\N
Dialogue: 0,1:33:01.76,1:33:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我觉得这个行为在集体中才能有更大的价值.\N因为这样才能得到"当你知道我的一切的时候,你还能向以前一样陪伴我,爱我吗"的答案?\Nbut I think the truth value is having confession in front of somebody else because then we force ourselves to say do you see me and do you still love me will you still be here if you fully know me that
Dialogue: 0,1:33:11.40,1:33:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得观察自身的最大的缺陷就是人永远看不到自己看不见的地方.\N你当然可以通过写作,通过观察自身,但有可能你看不见的地方你依然看不见\Nit's the most difficult part of yourself to observe is the place where you're most blind obviously and so you can journal and you can concentrate on yourself but that still might produce a situation where your blindest spots stay blind and
Dialogue: 0,1:33:31.00,1:33:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,而这也限制了你解决问题的方式,因为你只能使用自己的资源\Nalso it limits your ability to problem solve creatively because you only draw on your own resources
Dialogue: 0,1:33:38.40,1:33:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,而正常运转的婚姻的一个好处就是,但任何事情发生的时候,你们有两个大脑来思考\None of the wonderful things about a marriage that's functional is that both of you have two brains to work on to work out whatever problem happens to arise
Dialogue: 0,1:33:50.21,1:34:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,而婚姻生活难熬的有一部分原因就是,生活本身就很难熬.\N而婚姻要求你们一起面对生活中真实存在问题.这也是婚姻不同于约会的理由\Nand part of the reason that marriage is difficult is because life is difficult and you you have to jointly confront the actual problems of life which is what makes marriage different different than dating
Dialogue: 0,1:34:01.37,1:34:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,婚姻和出轨不同的在于,出轨是一种充满美好,没有任何问题的幻想.\Nfor example or different than an affair which is a you know a wish a wish fulfillment fantasy in some sense of all the intimacy with none of the problems
Dialogue: 0,1:34:10.42,1:34:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,这是个对你伴侣很糟糕的行为,因为你把问题都留给了他\Na very terrible thing to do to your partner who is then laden with only the problems
