Dialogue: 0,1:34:30.48,1:34:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,特别是,当你正在陷入和你精神健康有关系的自我认知的危机中\Nand so this is particularly true if you're in a solipsistic uh crisis in relationship to your mental health
